<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Making your first Phaser 3 Game - Part 1</title>
    <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/phaser/3.52.0/phaser.js"></script>
    <style>body {
            margin: 0;
        }</style>
</head>

<body>

    <script>var config = {
  type: Phaser.AUTO,
  width: 800,
  height: 600,
  scene: {
    preload: preload,
    create: create,
    update: update
  }
};
var game = new Phaser.Game(config);

function preload() {
  this.load.image('sky', 'assets/sky.png');
  this.load.image('ground', 'assets/platform.png');
  this.load.image('star', 'assets/star.png');
  this.load.image('bomb', 'assets/bomb.png');
  this.load.spritesheet('dude', 'assets/dude.png', {
    frameWidth: 32,
    frameHeight: 48
  });
}

function create() {
  this.add.image(500, 300, 'ground');
}

function update() {}</script>

</body>

</html>
